<h1>Directory of Geography Resources</h1>

    <p>
        <a href="/">Home</a> >
            <a href="/Kids_and_Teens">Kids and Teens</a>  >             <a href="/Kids_and_Teens/School_Time">School Time</a>  >             <a href="/Kids_and_Teens/School_Time/Social_Studies">Social Studies</a>  >             <a href="/Kids_and_Teens/School_Time/Social_Studies/Geography">Geography</a>         </p>

<p><p>Geography is the study of earth and its features. </p><p> This category lists sites that provide information or educational activities related to geography for <b> children and teenagers. </b></p></p>

<h2>Subcategories</h2>
